<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>{{ title }}</title>
<meta name="description" content="{{ description }}">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Libre+Caslon+Text:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Public+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="topstrip">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="mono">Mon–Fri 9 AM–6 PM · Sat 10 AM–2 PM EST</span>
    <span>Deadline approaching? <a href="tel:+17864085073">Call 786-408-5073 now</a></span>
  </div>
</div>

<header class="nav">
  <div class="wrap navbar">
    <a class="brand" href="/">
      <span class="brandmark">§</span>
      <span class="brandname">Writ Large<small>Federal Post-Conviction Resource</small></span>
    </a>
    <div class="nav-right">
      <nav class="links" aria-label="Main">
        <a href="/#services">Services</a>
        <a href="/blog/">Articles</a>
        <a href="/#tv">Videos</a>
        <a href="/litigation/">Full Lawsuit Support</a>
        <a class="callbtn" href="tel:+17864085073">Call 786-408-5073</a>
      </nav>
      <button class="hamburger" id="menuToggle" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="mobileMenu" aria-label="Open menu">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <nav class="mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu" aria-label="Mobile">
      <a href="/#services">Services</a>
      <a href="/blog/">Articles</a>
      <a href="/#tv">Videos</a>
      <a href="/litigation/">Full Lawsuit Support</a>
      <a href="/#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>
<script>
(function () {
  var btn = document.getElementById('menuToggle');
  var menu = document.getElementById('mobileMenu');
  if (!btn || !menu) return;
  btn.addEventListener('click', function () {
    var open = menu.classList.toggle('open');
    btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', open ? 'true' : 'false');
  });
})();
</script>


{{ content | safe }}
<footer class="site">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="cols">
      <div>
        <h4>Writ Large</h4>
        <p style="max-width:340px;line-height:1.7">A Prisoner Legal Aid resource. Federal post-conviction document preparation — § 2255 motions, § 2241 habeas petitions, and compassionate release — plus the news and education that comes with doing federal time.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Navigate</h4>
        <a href="/#services">Document Services</a>
        <a href="/blog/">Articles</a>
        <a href="/#tv">Videos</a>
        <a href="/litigation/">Full Lawsuit Support</a>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Contact</h4>
        <a href="tel:+17864085073">786-408-5073</a>
        <a href="mailto:info@prisonerlegalaid.com">info@prisonerlegalaid.com</a>
        <a href="https://prisonerlegalaid.com">prisonerlegalaid.com</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="disclaimer">
      © 2026 Writ Large, a Prisoner Legal Aid resource. All rights reserved. Writ Large provides paralegal document-preparation services for federal post-conviction matters. This is not legal representation and does not create an attorney-client relationship. Our writing team consists of accredited paralegals with experience in the federal system; we do not currently employ attorneys through Writ Large directly. No outcome, timeline, or result is guaranteed — courts, not Writ Large, decide the outcome of any motion. Clients remain responsible for reviewing, signing, and filing their own documents, and for all court deadlines, unless otherwise agreed in writing. If your matter may call for full attorney representation rather than document preparation, see how our <a href="/litigation/" style="text-decoration:underline">litigation support works</a>. This may be considered advertising in some jurisdictions.
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>


</body>
</html>
